actions.message:
Q: How do I become a combine/ota
A: You must ask an online SqL OR Staff member.

Q: How do I switch teams?
A: Make a new character with the unlocked job(s) you have.

Q: How do I open inventory?
A: Press tab, you'll figure it out eventually.

Q: Whats the server about and how do I join
A: We're a semi-serious RP with the Helix host, to connect to our server you must say in the console "connect nexushl2rp.hopto.org"

Q: I see Errors walking arround what do i do
A: Make sure you have all the stuff in this content pack installed as well as css and tf2 and hl2 
https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2278575292 

Q: How do i enable third person
A: Third person is enabled by entering ix_togglethirdperson

&Slap - Slaps a mentioned user

&flipcoin - the wonders of a coin flip

&gold - random thing i added
